email.subject: Boosting Your Business Potential Together
email.body:
Hello there,

I've been keeping an eye on your local business and I must say, I'm impressed by the consistent high reviews (4.6 rating, fantastic!). It's clear you're doing a sterling job at [location].

I understand that growth can seem daunting, but I have some simple yet effective review tactics that could potentially give your business a further lift. Would you fancy a quick chat or perhaps a coffee meeting to discuss this further? No pressure at all, just a friendly chat.

Looking forward to hearing from you soon.

Kind regards,
